# REST Client file Architect

### Create a new bus
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/architect/buses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZW1haWwiOiJqb2huLmRvZUBlbWFpbC5jb20iLCJpc0FkbWluIjp0cnVlLCJpYXQiOjE3ODE3MzI2MzMsImV4cCI6MTc4MTc0MzQzM30.FpbmukBaGlaB83bUQHapdPws4S6vlbbvCPIA36aERVh2wCMgK8U8huIN24e4w5do

{
  "plateNumber": "fka-4902",
  "totalCapacity": 40,
  "isActive": true
}

